{
  "stem": "802.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father had some purified gold, you know, that didn't have any-- any other metals in it, and he gave it to them to buy weapons.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as you probably know, no one wanted to give us weapons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No one offered us any help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The whole world was totally indifferent to our tragedy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think it's unprecedented.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I think, perhaps, they have learned to help, like, Cambodia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know how much they helped there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But in other places, there was some help to rescue people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And all the doors were closed to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And weapons, you know, we pleaded with the Poles to give us weapons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Obviously they didn't have too many either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But they were shipped from England, because the Polish government went to England, fled to England.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they would not cooperate with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so-- I mean, we could've fought together against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they did not do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, to go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All right, so then we are now in-- on Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK, my father is savagely beaten.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we are all terrified and very, very hungry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they packed us into the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Really, literally, it's not an exaggeration, like sardines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was hardly any room for breathing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They sent us to Majdanek, which is in-- in Lublin-- Lublin, which is 'Lubleen,' as one would pronounce it, perhaps, in English.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which is not too far from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it took us about three or four days and nights to get there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very typical of all the trains with the-- with the victims, you know, with-- with-- with those whom they were going to kill, to take these extended, long hours of getting to the place.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because in some way, this disarmed us too, emotionally and physically.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
